text: Þonne þu on morgen ærest arise gemune þu þone halgan heahengel sanctus michael on þinum mode & gebide þe to him.
& singgloria in <excelsis> deo& credan &pater noster& þas þreo fers,Benedicite, Benedicite, <Benedicite>.
Þonne hafast ðu blisse on þone dæg ægðer ge for gode ge for worulde, amen.
